2 Kings - Young&rsquo;s Literal Translation (YLT) [1:1] And Moab transgresseth against Israel after the death of Ahab,
[1:2] and Ahaziah falleth through the lattice in his upper chamber that is' in Samaria, and is sick, and sendeth messengers, and saith unto them, Go ye, inquire of Baal-Zebub god of Ekron if I recover from this sickness.&rsquo;
[1:3] And a messenger of Jehovah hath spoken unto Elijah the Tishbite, `Rise, go up to meet the messengers of the king of Samaria, and speak unto them, Is it because there is not a God in Israel &ndash; ye are going to inquire of Baal Zebub god of Ekron?
